1. Upload limit of one file per request.
2. PDF filename is shorter than 50 characters.
3. The file key in the request header is 'file'
4. Each PDF filename is unique, since they are identified by their names.
5. URLs must start with an http:\\ or https:\\
6. Requesting URL info for a specific document should include the document's name.
    i.e. requesting /doc/test.pdf will send info for the test.pdf document.